opic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Schematic overview 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Real example 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-715CA573-7523-417C-9AC3-3FB5A44DF0D2" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-DABE337D-089F-44FF-9155-A0B5D9D37F65-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-DABE337D-089F-44FF-9155-A0B5D9D37F65-low.png"/></fig></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-FA9D64FB-6054-489E-9DB8-5230544CF200" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-F217D87B-B2C4-4D63-B622-976CA9563F1C-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-F217D87B-B2C4-4D63-B622-976CA9563F1C-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-70AB8BC6-D014-4D00-BFEA-34BB9E27EFCC" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-45F677BF-4DAA-4D43-91E6-8FC55A996D01-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-45F677BF-4DAA-4D43-91E6-8FC55A996D01-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-EC1EAE23-40EC-4B10-A2C9-83873F76DC70" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Collect</title><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Symptoms</b> 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Light sharp lines and/or dotted pattern which repeats in media direction 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Pattern is visible during complete print (even &gt;1 meter) 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> The pattern can also be a continuous band. The edges of the band are hard-defined. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Multiple patterns may be visible over the width of the print 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> The repeating distance of the pattern is independent of the used print mode. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> The existence of the light lines and/or dotted can be dependent on the used media 
</p></li></ul><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Functional logging (if available)</b> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">No logging available which can pinpoint to this case. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">ADAM-triggers</b> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">No ADAM-triggers available. 
</p></section><section id="GUID-DDCC1BB0-B402-4010-9156-67DB737F3DE5" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Analyze/Repair</title><fig id="GUID-62E38E82-2EC2-4096-8E14-F1057A645872" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-7AA1D8B7-FE1B-40C5-BCE2-89F20C217791-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-7AA1D8B7-FE1B-40C5-BCE2-89F20C217791-svg.svg"/></fig><table pgwide="1" id="GUID-7BA41B15-9C22-427B-8E94-9405DD00EFE1" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="4" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="15.50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="20*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col4" colnum="4" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Type 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">To do 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Before print a new job. Clean part of the media which showed issues in the previous print. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> First clean the surface of the media using a dry (and clean) cloth 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> Secondly clean a part of the media using Isopropyl Alcohol. 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Decision 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Check whether the cleaning did prevent or alter the issue. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-905500D7-AE08-4E2B-BF9D-A6E697DDA439" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-33E2DF9E-0D88-4EF8-A872-2E6F6DB564A2-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-33E2DF9E-0D88-4EF8-A872-2E6F6DB564A2-low.png"/></fig><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Measure the distance between the repeating patterns. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Determine the distance of the pattern towards the center of the print. 
</p></li></ol></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Use other (non-polluted media) 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> In case of a repeating pattern measure the distance as shown in the figure. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Decision 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Check whether the position and distance can be found in the table below. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Clean or replace the regarding roller 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">7 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Most likely the media is mechanical damaged. Use other media 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-BB9BDDD1-E29C-42C5-BF10-2854E3AE4223" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Specific patterns and positions (see step 5):</title><table pgwide="1" id="GUID-D963269B-E108-446A-A212-4581FEAA8740" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="4" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="20*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col4" colnum="4" colwidth="30*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step distance 
