</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">44 mm 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">All widths (every 50 mm, 10 mm in width) 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">X-tran roller 
