</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Only center (+/- 30 mm) 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Upper MLO-roller 
